<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.8.8">
<l>oṟṟaik kuḻaiyum nāñcilu morupāl tōṉṟat tāṉtōṉṟi</l>
<l>veṟṟit toḻilār vēlvēntar viṇpāṟ cella veñcamattu</l>
<l>ceṟṟa koṟṟat toḻilāṉaic centī mūṉṟu milliruppa</l>
<l>kaṟṟa maṟaiyōr kaṇṇapurat taṭiyēṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The man of endeavor who conquered spear[-bearing] kings</l>
<l rend="indent">to kill [them] in heated battle,</l>
<l>So those whose endeavor was victory went to heaven,</l>
<l rend="indent">having appeared himself</l>
<l>When he [also] appeared with a plough at one side</l>
<l rend="indent">and a single earring,</l>
<l>I, his servant, saw for myself in Kaṇṇapuram with learned Vedic experts</l>
<l rend="indent">as the three blazing fires endure in the houses.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
